      <title>“闰年故障”导致新西兰部分燃油泵关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/leap-year-glitch-shuts-some-new-zealand-fuel-pumps-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加油站和支付服务提供商表示，由于支付软件出现“闰年故障”，新西兰一些加油站周四停止工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/leap-year-glitch-shuts-some-new-zealand-fuel-pumps-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 03:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部长称中国向巴基斯坦提供20亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rolls-over-2-bln-loan-pakistan-finance-minister-says-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[看守财政部长沙姆沙德·阿赫塔尔周四在回应路透社时证实，中国已向巴基斯坦提供了 20 亿美元贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rolls-over-2-bln-loan-pakistan-finance-minister-says-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 02:39:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰将审查排放交易计划的林业部分</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-review-forestry-component-emission-trading-scheme-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府周四表示，将对该国排放交易计划林业部分的相关成本进行独立审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-review-forestry-component-emission-trading-scheme-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹恩惠将于周四会见 Meta 的扎克伯格</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-koreas-president-yoon-meet-metas-zuckerberg-thursday-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈 (Yoon Suk Yeol) 办公室表示，周四将与 Meta 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 会面，韩国科技巨头正在寻求与这家美国公司在人工智能等领域建立潜在的业务合作关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/south-koreas-president-yoon-meet-metas-zuckerberg-thursday-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:57:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高级部长表示，印度尼西亚计划在两到三年内成为经合组织成员国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-aims-become-oecd-member-2-3-years-senior-minister-says-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级内阁部长周三晚间表示，印度尼西亚计划在两到三年内完成加入总部位于巴黎的经济合作与发展组织（OECD）的成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-aims-become-oecd-member-2-3-years-senior-minister-says-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚第四季度商业投资环比增长0.8%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-q4-business-investment-rises-08-qq-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于采矿业的进一步增长，澳大利亚商业投资在去年第四季度升至八年新高，同时升级了未来支出计划以推动经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-q4-business-investment-rises-08-qq-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:47:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜金正恩在不平等加剧的情况下寻求农村地区的“产业革命”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-seeks-industry-revolution-rural-areas-amid-widening-inequality-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官方媒体朝中社周四表示，在长期粮食短缺和经济不平等加剧的情况下，朝鲜领导人金正恩呼吁在全国范围内建设工厂，在农村地区进行“工业革命”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-seeks-industry-revolution-rural-areas-amid-widening-inequality-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:45:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓将重组部分全球企业角色以削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bhp-restructure-some-global-corporate-roles-it-looks-trim-costs-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的上市矿业公司必和必拓集团周四表示，将解散部分全球团队，并将规划、环境和遗产保护等职能转移至矿业资产管理部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bhp-restructure-some-global-corporate-roles-it-looks-trim-costs-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚1月份零售额反弹1.1%，趋势依然疲弱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-retail-sales-bounce-11-jan-trend-still-weak-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚零售销售在上个月低迷后于 1 月份出现反弹，但由于高利率侵蚀了消费能力，年度支出增长仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-retail-sales-bounce-11-jan-trend-still-weak-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾马科斯表示他将坚定捍卫主权</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-he-remains-firm-defending-sovereignty-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周四在澳大利亚议会表示，他不会允许任何外国势力夺取该国“一平方英寸”的领土，马尼拉将坚定捍卫其主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-he-remains-firm-defending-sovereignty-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:12:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
